data.description: Discover an impeccably maintained Beautiful Ranch Style, one-story single-family home sitting on a 26,500 LOT. This GEM features, 4 bedrooms ,2 remodeled bathrooms, spacious closets, tile & vinyl flooring throughout, and a remodeled kitchen with stainless steel appliances. New AC installed 08/2022. Roof replaced 2015. Large family room with French doors that lead to a breathtaking backyard oasis, 7 fruit trees, garden stations, an oversized covered paved patio, fire pit, wooden deck. Concrete shed with electricity. That's not all, there is a bonus room (perfect for guest, in-laws, studio, etc...). No HOA. Move-in perfect! All offers considered, Sellers Motivated.
